'''Tusnakt''' d tussna yimḍanen s umata, tettwa sileɣ s tmusniwin timadwanin (''connaissances abstraites'') s tallat n [[Azebz|izebzan]] [[Tameẓla|imeẓlan]] (''raisonnements logiques'') ɣef [[tamiḍrant|tmiḍranin]] (''concepts'') am [[amḍan|yimḍanen]] (''nombres''), [[tanezgit]] (''géométrie''), [[tiskiwt (tusnakt)|tiskiwin]] (''structures'') neɣ [[iseɣwal inezgiyen|iseɣwal]] (''transformation''). Tusnakt tbedd daɣen ɣef taɣult n [[tagmi tusnit|tegmi]] (''recherche'') iy ssendalen (''developpe'') timusniwin, akk d wayen it sselmad.

